<sect1 id="rni18">
    <title>Internationalization</title>

    <para>
    Thanks to members of the worldwide <ulink
    url="http://developer.gnome.org/projects/gtp/">GNOME Translation
    Project</ulink>, under the leadership of Christian Rose and Danilo Å egan,
    GNOME &version; offers support for 43 languages (at least 80 percent of
    strings translated).

