  <para>Note that Galician, Estonian, Indonesian, Macedonian, Nepali, Slovak, Vietnamese, Thai, and Xhosa
  are new supported languages in GNOME &version;,
  thanks to the hard work of their translators. Also worthy of mention is that British English
  and Canadian English are also supported.</para>
  
  <para>Many other languages are partially supported, with more than half of
  their strings translated.</para>

